                        <interp inst="t18540130-name-160" type="given" value="SAMUEL"></interp>SAMUEL WHEELER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, E</hi> 126). I took the prisoner on 21st Jan.—I received this crown piece.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
